1 row in set (0.00 sec)

mysql> SELECT YEAR(NOW()), MONTH(NOW()), DAY(NOW()), HOUR(NOW()), MINUTE(NOW()), SECOND(NOW());
+-------------+--------------+------------+-------------+---------------+---------------+
| YEAR(NOW()) | MONTH(NOW()) | DAY(NOW()) | HOUR(NOW()) | MINUTE(NOW()) | SECOND(NOW()) |
+-------------+--------------+------------+-------------+---------------+---------------+
|        2018 |           11 |          8 |          17 |            19 |            31 |
+-------------+--------------+------------+-------------+---------------+---------------+
1 row in set (0.00 sec)

